Greetings, Retricans!
We are here to make Retrica awesome. If you have any questions or inquiries, please email us at contact@retrica.co

***NEW***
- Let the Hashtag Challenge begin! Tag your selfie with different hashtag everyday and share with Retrica community. (Log-in required)
- Do you like mystery? You can now set your gender as secret.
- Don’t like the noise in your video? You can mute the sound of your video in Review.

***FIXED***
- We've fixed minor bugs here and there for more stable selfie time.

Team Retrica
with love!

- With YOLO filter pack, turn your selfie into lomo arts!

- You can mention your friends in your selfie now. Simply type "@username" or "@fullname" in text mode!

+ [RE-1206] Some photo looked blurry in My Memories

You might want to sit down for this one because we've added a whole lotta new stuff in this version. We've also got a new look and a whole new messaging feature! So many reasons to update.

[v. 6.0.0]
• A new look and feel that's easier to use
• The Alert tab now includes private messaging for your friends on Retrica
• The curated "For You" feed sends the best pictures on Retrica straight to you
• Bug fixes and usability improvements

Also we're sad to announce MyMemories cloud storage support will end soon. You can still access any and all of your MyMemories in this version until the end of September, 2018. Download any pictures you want to keep before then.
